This just in!!! 🥳 Roxxi and Nevra, your fave Bratz couple, are officially available for purchase online at Amazon.com and  Walmart.com, and coming soon to Target! This super stylin’ 2 pack features the couple steppin’ out and comin’ out in their scorchin’ pride rally looks to fight for LOVE in all forms! Our girls were designed in collaboration with LGBTQ fashion designer @lovejimmypaul, and are coupled with a $25K donation through MGA Cares to The Trevor Project, the world’s largest suicide prevention and mental health organization for LGBTQ youth. Make sure to stay tuned for info on official Jimmy Paul x Bratz apparel, also launching soon! 👄🌈 #bratz
